{"tid":865954,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"返嚟喇！ 雲加公佈1‧1回歸","createTime":"2018-10-17T13:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T11:39:50.000Z","uid":138762,"like":137,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"ca51b7d93b83dc2f5c71587a612f7404049b8200","tid":865954,"uid":138762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T13:21:02.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=v7SFhVMdNLZxt93nRRuBXP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=da7fde6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】放心，未退休！前阿仙奴領隊雲加公佈將於來年1月回歸球壇，落腳地似乎是國際舞台或日本球壇。<br />\n<br />\n68歲的雲加（Arsene Wenger）今年夏天與阿仙奴結束22年情，休養生息，準備接受下一個挑戰。他接受《圖片報》訪問時說：「我相信會在2019年1月1日重新展開領隊生涯，但我目前未知下一站去向，仍在休息，但已準備隨時上班。」<br />\n<br />\n雲加一度傳出返回法國，擔任巴黎聖日耳門的經理，但最終不了了之。「名單上有國家隊，也可能回到日本。」雲加的去向備受關注，但相信不少球迷仍希望「教授」最終留在歐洲球壇，「感謝在阿仙奴的22年歲月，任何方面都令我提升不少。」<br />\n<br />\n雲加贏過3次英超冠軍、7次足總盃冠軍，但最經典的一季，自然是2003/04率阿仙奴成為前無古人的不敗之師。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd9916a91ef47f6a61063b003ce65457210fc85","tid":865954,"uid":30476,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T13:24:22.000Z","msg":"感謝在阿仙奴的22年歲月，任何方面都令我提升不少<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b07584ea06b1bbb338f46bd8e186ade2da1953","tid":865954,"uid":45335,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T13:24:58.000Z","msg":"雲加想開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa18aed9f05fafe23ba1a372917d8bb8246999c","tid":865954,"uid":5549,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T13:25:56.000Z","msg":"教國家隊就最岩"},{"pid":"1b3b9272e4f511f9276f97497429adeb2a5870ac","tid":865954,"uid":581,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T13:30:36.000Z","msg":"曼聯準備1月1炒